  [seq1 seq2]

  ([coll1 coll2]
    (intrlv coll1 coll2 '()))
    ([coll1 coll2 acc]    
      (let [acc2 (if (empty? coll1)
                      acc
                      (concat acc (list (first coll1))))
            acc3 (if (empty? coll2)
                      acc2
                      (concat acc2 (list (first coll2))))
            ncoll1 (if (empty? coll1)
                      coll1
                      (rest coll1))
            ncoll2 (if (empty? coll2)

        (if (or (empty? coll1) (empty? coll2))
          acc
          (recur ncoll1 ncoll2 acc3)))))

(fn [data1 data2]
    (let [g (fn [res d1 d2 left]
              (cond
                (and left (seq d1) (seq d2))
                (recur (conj res (first d1)) d2 (rest d1) false)
                (and (not left) (seq d1))
                (recur (conj res (first d1)) d2 (rest d1) true)
                :else res))]
      (g [] data1 data2 true)))

(fn ileave [& seqs]
  (let [makebatch (fn [seqs] (loop [firsts [] rests [] work seqs]
                               (if (not (seq work))
                                 ;; We are done.
                                 [firsts rests]
                                 ;; We have more sequences to look through.
                                 (let [this_seq (first work)
                                       next_seq (next this_seq)]
                                   (recur
                                     (conj firsts (first this_seq))
                                     (when
                                       (and
                                         (not (nil? rests))
                                         (seq next_seq))
                                       (conj rests next_seq))
                                     (next work))))))
        batchiter (fn batchiter [seqs]
                    (let [[firsts rests] (makebatch seqs)]
                      (if (nil? rests)
                        (conj firsts rests)
                        (lazy-seq (conj firsts (batchiter rests))))))
        unroll (fn unroll [batches]
                  (let [results (butlast batches)
                        remaining (last batches)]
                    (if (nil? remaining)
                      results
                      (lazy-seq (concat results (unroll remaining)))
                      )))]
    (unroll (batchiter seqs))))
